cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques to recover 3D shape structures from single RGB images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and rendering techniques, which makes cs.GR (Computer Graphics) another likely category. The paper uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category. The paper also involves training and optimization of neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Finally, the paper involves 3D modeling and reconstruction, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category.
